{"tid":154644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳克儉：不認為政協入校是洗腦","createTime":"2017-03-13T12:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T02:05:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d32280426e9d1a69532ac85ae74f14203d956271","tid":154644,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】教育局局吳克儉不認為政協走入校園開展國情教育活動是洗腦，相信熟悉基本法人士可以支援學校，而教育界立法會議員葉建源則認為，這是不恰當的政治決定。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長吳克儉回應，全國政協鼓勵委員走入香港校園開展國情教育，他不認同這是洗腦，歡迎熟悉基本法人士支援學校。<br />\n<br />\n政府近年透過不同途徑投放資源讓學生認識國情。<br />\n<br />\n2012年國教爭議，教育局擱置德育及國民教育科，課程指引前已向全港每所中、小學及特殊學校發放53萬元一筆過津貼。<br />\n<br />\n隨後在2015年施政報告，又提出資助學生於中、小學階段最少各一次到內地交流，預計至17/18學年，資助額達1.1億。<br />\n<br />\n除了教育局，民政事務局亦有資助青年到內地交流或實習，於校外推廣國民教育。<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源認為，再鼓勵政協走進校園是不恰當的政治決定。他認為教育工作者有專業判斷，不應受到政治干擾。"},{"pid":"fea82840f89498bdf8cc1b5fa143d0b8eea531fd","tid":154644,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"片：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=213938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D213938&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f73e9d14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D213938&h=f679fbf1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=213938</a>"},{"pid":"96cc68936a82ef6338b8ed36616a409100fd38f0","tid":154644,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T12:35:01.000Z","msg":"黨委 when?"},{"pid":"f786897b5f3ecade35206ca46bcdfbdf40d3fe36","tid":154644,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"幾時死"},{"pid":"3c227e746c4bb72f282c6fbb3de110a39a62f0ec","tid":154644,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"我認為係喎"},{"pid":"567a547b414b9baf5459affea75148f1dd74902e","tid":154644,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"吳克儉呢個人絕對可以寫入香港歷史"},{"pid":"85bf53273772472013ccfbf493b764e04cbf1ffd","tid":154644,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581f4ee6ba1a1c148863f38fbc9ed37e62080bf9","tid":154644,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"吳克殮死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50690841ed1517b9880d61219f43faf29ddd525","tid":154644,"uid":1455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吳克殮死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經死左老母同老婆，好似仲有2個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}